{
  "book": 20,
  "chapter": 8,
  "sections": [
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "heading": "智慧頌"
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 1,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Does not wisdom cry out, And understanding lift up her voice? "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 1,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Does not wisdom cry out, And understanding lift up her voice?"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 1,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 2,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "She takes her stand on the top of the high hill, Beside the way, where the paths meet. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 2,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "She takes her stand on the top of the high hill, Beside the way, where the paths meet."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 2,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 3,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "She cries out by the gates, at the entry of the city, At the entrance of the doors: "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 3,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "She cries out by the gates, at the entry of the city, At the entrance of the doors:"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 3,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 4,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "“To you, O men, I call, And my voice is to the sons of men. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 4,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "“To you, O men, I call, And my voice is to the sons of men."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 4,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 5,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "O you simple ones, understand prudence, And you fools, be of an understanding heart. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 5,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "O you simple ones, understand prudence, And you fools, be of an understanding heart."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 5,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 6,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Listen, for I will speak of excellent things, And from the opening of my lips will  come right things; "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 6,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Listen, for I will speak of excellent things, And from the opening of my lips will  come right things;"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 6,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 7,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "For my mouth will speak truth; Wickedness is an abomination to my lips. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 7,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "For my mouth will speak truth; Wickedness is an abomination to my lips."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 7,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 8,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "All the words of my mouth are with righteousness; Nothing crooked or perverse is in them. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 8,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "All the words of my mouth are with righteousness; Nothing crooked or perverse is in them."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 8,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 9,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "They are all plain to him who understands, And right to those who find knowledge. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 9,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "They are all plain to him who understands, And right to those who find knowledge."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 9,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 10,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Receive my instruction, and not silver, And knowledge rather than choice gold; "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 10,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Receive my instruction, and not silver, And knowledge rather than choice gold;"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 10,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 11,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "For wisdom is better than rubies, And all the things one may desire cannot be compared with her. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 11,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "For wisdom is better than rubies, And all the things one may desire cannot be compared with her."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 11,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 12,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "“I, wisdom, dwell with prudence, And find out knowledge and discretion. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 12,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "“I, wisdom, dwell with prudence, And find out knowledge and discretion."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 12,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 13,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "The fear of the Lord  is to hate evil; Pride and arrogance and the evil way And the perverse mouth I hate. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 13,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "The fear of the Lord  is to hate evil; Pride and arrogance and the evil way And the perverse mouth I hate."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 13,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "The fear of the Lord  is to hate evil; Pride and arrogance and the evil way And the perverse mouth I hate."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 13,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 14,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Counsel is mine, and sound wisdom; I am understanding, I have strength. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 14,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Counsel is mine, and sound wisdom; I am understanding, I have strength."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 14,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 15,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "By me kings reign, And rulers decree justice. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 15,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "By me kings reign, And rulers decree justice."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 15,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 16,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "By me princes rule, and nobles, All the judges of the earth. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 16,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "By me princes rule, and nobles, All the judges of the earth."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 16,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 17,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "I love those who love me, And those who seek me diligently will find me. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 17,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "I love those who love me, And those who seek me diligently will find me."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 17,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 18,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Riches and honor are with me, Enduring riches and righteousness. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 18,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Riches and honor are with me, Enduring riches and righteousness."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 18,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 19,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "My fruit is better than gold, yes, than fine gold, And my revenue than choice silver. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 19,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "My fruit is better than gold, yes, than fine gold, And my revenue than choice silver."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 19,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 20,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "I traverse the way of righteousness, In the midst of the paths of justice, "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 20,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "I traverse the way of righteousness, In the midst of the paths of justice,"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 20,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 21,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "That I may cause those who love me to inherit wealth, That I may fill their treasuries. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 21,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "That I may cause those who love me to inherit wealth, That I may fill their treasuries."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 21,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 22,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "“The  Lord possessed me at the beginning of His way, Before His works of old. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 22,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "“The  Lord possessed me at the beginning of His way, Before His works of old."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 22,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 23,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "I have been established from everlasting, From the beginning, before there was ever an earth. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 23,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "I have been established from everlasting, From the beginning, before there was ever an earth."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 23,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 24,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "When there  were no depths I was brought forth, When there  were no fountains abounding with water. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 24,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "When there  were no depths I was brought forth, When there  were no fountains abounding with water."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 24,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 25,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Before the mountains were settled, Before the hills, I was brought forth; "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 25,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Before the mountains were settled, Before the hills, I was brought forth;"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 25,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 26,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "While as yet He had not made the earth or the fields, Or the primal dust of the world. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 26,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "While as yet He had not made the earth or the fields, Or the primal dust of the world."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 26,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 27,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "When He prepared the heavens, I was there, When He drew a circle on the face of the deep, "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 27,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "When He prepared the heavens, I was there, When He drew a circle on the face of the deep,"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 27,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 28,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "When He established the clouds above, When He strengthened the fountains of the deep, "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 28,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "When He established the clouds above, When He strengthened the fountains of the deep,"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 28,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 29,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "When He assigned to the sea its limit, So that the waters would not transgress His command, When He marked out the foundations of the earth, "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 29,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "When He assigned to the sea its limit, So that the waters would not transgress His command, When He marked out the foundations of the earth,"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 29,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 30,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Then I was beside Him as a master craftsman; And I was daily His delight, Rejoicing always before Him, "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 30,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Then I was beside Him as a master craftsman; And I was daily His delight, Rejoicing always before Him,"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 30,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Then I was beside Him as a master craftsman; And I was daily His delight, Rejoicing always before Him,"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 30,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 31,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Rejoicing in His inhabited world, And my delight was with the sons of men. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 31,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Rejoicing in His inhabited world, And my delight was with the sons of men."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 31,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 32,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "“Now therefore, listen to me, my children, For blessed are  those  who keep my ways. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 32,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "“Now therefore, listen to me, my children, For blessed are  those  who keep my ways."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 32,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 33,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Hear instruction and be wise, And do not disdain it. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 33,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Hear instruction and be wise, And do not disdain it."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 33,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 34,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Blessed is the man who listens to me, Watching daily at my gates, Waiting at the posts of my doors. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 34,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Blessed is the man who listens to me, Watching daily at my gates, Waiting at the posts of my doors."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 34,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 35,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "For whoever finds me finds life, And obtains favor from the Lord; "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 35,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "For whoever finds me finds life, And obtains favor from the Lord;"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 35,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 36,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "But he who sins against me wrongs his own soul; All those who hate me love death.” "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 36,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "But he who sins against me wrongs his own soul; All those who hate me love death.”"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}